daw-acoustics
=============

This module is a pure-Java port of the RoomAcoustiCpp room acoustics
library and is therefore a derivative work for the purposes of the
GNU General Public License, version 3 (GPLv3).

Original work
-------------
  Name    : RoomAcoustiCpp
  Version : 1.0.1
  Author  : Fraunhofer IIS / Audio Labs
  Website : https://github.com/audiolabs/RoomAcoustiCpp
  License : GNU General Public License (GPL), version 3

Derivative work
---------------
  Module  : daw-acoustics
  Path    : src/main/java/com/benesquivelmusic/daw/acoustics/
  License : GNU General Public License (GPL), version 3
            (see the project root LICENSE file for the full text)

Per GPLv3 §5, this derivative work is distributed under the same GPLv3
license as the original. The "Ported from RoomAcoustiCpp {@code …}"
Javadoc comments throughout this module identify the C++ classes that
each Java class is derived from.

The vendored C++ source tree (formerly at lib/RoomAcoustiCpp-1.0.1/)
has been removed from this repository now that the Java port is
complete. The original upstream sources remain available at the
Website URL above.

Intentionally not ported (out of scope for a pure-Java DAW):
  - Unity plugin bridge
  - Windows Visual Studio project files
  - Android NDK project files
  - moodycamel lock-free queue (replaced by java.util.concurrent)
  - AudioThreadPool / SpinLock (replaced by java.util.concurrent.locks)
  - Timer / ScopedTimer / RACProfiler (use JFR / Micrometer instead)
